<h3>Azur Lane Early to Mid Game Farming Fleet</h3>
<p>For the front line we use (from left to right) <a href="https://azurlane.koumakan.jp/Portland">Portland</a>,
<a href="https://azurlane.koumakan.jp/Cleveland">Cleveland</a>, and <a href="https://azurlane.koumakan.jp/Indianapolis">
Indianapolis</a>. For the back line we use (from left to right) <a href="https://azurlane.koumakan.jp/Shouhou">Shouhou</a>,
<a href="https://azurlane.koumakan.jp/Unicorn">Unicorn</a>, and <a href="https://azurlane.koumakan.jp/Arizona">Arizona</a>.</p>
<h5>Main Guns</h5>
<p>Portland and Indianapolis are both <a href="https://azurlane.koumakan.jp/Glossary">Heavy Cruisers (CAs)</a>
and hence should equip either <em>Twin 203mm Main Gun (SK C)</em> for AP or a <em>203mm Mounted Gun</em>
for HE. Cleveland is a <a href="https://azurlane.koumakan.jp/Glossary">Light Cruiser (CL)</a>
and should equip a <em>Twin 150mm Main Gun (Tbtsk C/36)</em> for AP or <em>Triple 155mm Mounted Gun</em> for HE.
Only pick the AP gun if the HE gun is not available to you yet.</p>
<p>Arizona is a <a href="https://azurlane.koumakan.jp/Glossary">Battle Ship (BB)</a> and receives either a
<em>Triple 406mm MK6</em> (max DPS) or <em>Twin 410mm</em> (max Fire Rate). As Arizona heals with main
gun volleys, choose fire rate over dps.</p>
<p>
<h5>Secondary Guns</h5>
<p>The frontline girls and Arizona should use a Purple or Gold <em>Twin 127mm MK12 Dual Gun</em> for HE.</p>
<h5>Anti Air Guns</h5>
<p><em>Twin 113mm AA Gun</em> or <em>Quadruple 40mm Bofors Gun</em> are top tier anti air guns
for any class in any line.</p>
<h5>Auxiliaries</h5>
<p>Each frontline girl should be equipped with a <em>Repair Toolkit</em> and a <em>Torpedo Buldge</em>.
The Light Carriers Shouhou and Unicorn each receive an <em>Aviation Oil Tank</em> or <em>Steam Catapult</em> (whichever provides more AA).
Shouhou equips the <em>Beaver Squad Tag</em> whilst Unicorn receives another <em>Aviation Oil Tank</em>/<em>Steam Catapult</em>.
</p>
<p>Arizona equips a <em>High-Standard Fire-Control Radar</em> to further decrease the reload time of her main gun volley and an <em>SG Radar</em>.</p>
